ActExport and Import Permits Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Import Control List
PrecisOrder amending the IMPORT CONTROL LIST (ICL) in order to include carbon and specialty steel products on the ICL to implement Canada's commitments set out in the Joint Statement with respect to monitoring of steel trade.
